description:
Kate brightens up her home with flowers and Doree’s bitten by the baking bug. Then they hear from many listeners about their experiences with menstrual cups/discs, and how to make it through the rest of the election season. Plus, they receive a very sweet long-distance song dedication.


 Activity of the Day: Make sure you’re registered to vote! Vote early if you can!


To leave a voicemail or text for a future episode, reach us at 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.
